        {
            "title": "川普稱若中國嚴打芬太尼出口 美國願取消相關關稅",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國總統唐納德·川普表示，如果中國嚴厲打擊芬太尼及其前體化學品的出口，他願意取消所有與芬太尼相關的對華商品關稅。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普周五表示，他與中國國家主席習近平在韓國會晤時討論了這一問題，並稱「中國正在非常努力地應對，我真心認為他們有動力這麼做」。川普在元首會晤中同意將與芬太尼相關的20%關稅減半。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「一旦我們看到這一點，我們將取消剩下的10%，」川普在空軍一號上對記者說。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這番言論預示著川普在未來的貿易談判中可能會對中國作出另一項讓步。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-415286fd-67d7-3363-ac1e-9b579d112ee7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：川普就中國暫停稀土管制一事自誇戰功 專家則稱開了危險的先例</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中美兩國領導人本周達成具有里程碑意義的休戰協議。根據協議，川普放棄了對中國商品加徵100%關稅的威脅，並暫停對中國船隻徵收港口費，此外還降低了芬太尼關稅並採取了其他措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">作為交換，中國暫緩收緊稀土磁體出口的計畫，並恢復採購大豆在內的美國農產品。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些措施旨在持續一年，屆時雙方將再次進行談判。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我認為，我們將與他保持長期的良好關係，」川普在談及習近平時告訴記者。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Says US Would Lift China Fentanyl Tariff If Xi Cracks Down</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Skylar Woodhouse.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E7%A8%B1%E8%8B%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9A%B4%E6%89%93%E8%8A%AC%E5%A4%AA%E5%B0%BC%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%A3-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%A1%98%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E7%9B%B8%E9%97%9C%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-165612387.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-01 01:26:06",
